Show HN: Zukini – Simple browser grocery/reminder list
text:
Hi HN!

Often when my wife and I try to order groceries online, we have to maintain a bit of a grocery list of items that we thought up over the week. But we also sometimes forget what's on the list when we're trying to put the order in (because it's out of sight, meaning it's often out of mind as well).

I thought I just might make this simple extension to see if it's of any use to myself and others. Originally I wanted to have a shared sync functionality so that we could both just put in the same "list key" and we'd sync each other's list online, but it seems I'll have to make my own service to support that, which will come soon.

If it interests you, try it out and let me know what you think! This is the first time I've ever "released" something so I hope you enjoy and/or share some feedback.
